<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">We strive to make this an enjoyable online resource and provide quality information to all its visitors.</h4>
[/ultimate_heading][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_row equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]This is about a group of young people who spent the greater part of a day together strictly because they were of the same age and lived in the same vicinity. Learning from teachers about how to read, write, work with numbers, know where we came from and how to work and get along with others were the goals they sought. Along the way, friendships developed and life-changing experiences that shaped us–occurred. It is the goal of this site to compile some of those experiences and memories. Collectively, by sharing each person’s view of what they remember, can we all enjoy the re-living of our formative years.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][ve_progress_bar bgcolor=\"custom\" css_animation=\"zoomIn\" field=\"Your Involvment\" percentage=\"80\" custombarcolor=\"#1abc9c\"][ve_progress_bar bgcolor=\"custom\" css_animation=\"zoomIn\" field=\"Your Memnory\" percentage=\"58\" custombarcolor=\"#ccab1c\"][ve_progress_bar bgcolor=\"custom\" css_animation=\"zoomIn\" field=\"Your Life\'s Experiences\" percentage=\"75\" custombarcolor=\"#cc571c\"][ve_progress_bar bgcolor=\"custom\" css_animation=\"zoomIn\" field=\"Add Up To Pure Enjoyment !\" percentage=\"100\" custombarcolor=\"#121f5b\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"bottom\" bg_type=\"bg_color\" bg_color_value=\"#dbdbdb\"][vc_column][vc_wp_text]
<blockquote>
<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">We hope you enjoy the website and reflect back to what seemed like simpler times. It can be better, though, if you participate in helping provide more content–only then will it help add more of what is needed–memories that make us smile.(visit the Info/Faq page on how you can contribute) Please be kind, visit often, contribute what you remember, and help us spread the word!</h3>
