("4877","1","2018-07-17 10:00:59","2018-07-17 10:00:59","[vc_section][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" bg_type=\"image\" parallax_style=\"vcpb-default\" bg_image_new=\"id^4457|url^http://1969tigers.co.events/s/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Tiger-3blk.png|caption^null|alt^null|title^Tiger 3blk|description^null\" parallax_content=\"parallax_content_value\" parallax_content_sense=\"70\" enable_overlay=\"enable_overlay_value\" overlay_pattern=\"03.png\" css=\".vc_custom_1531033314432{border-top-width: 170px !important;padding-bottom: 130px !important;}\"][vc_column][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"In Memoriam\" main_heading_color=\"#eded10\" sub_heading_color=\"#81d742\" main_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Aladin|font_call:Aladin\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:50px;tablet:30px;tablet_portrait:25px;mobile_landscape:20px;mobile:20px;\" sub_heading_font_size=\"desktop:24px;tablet:16px;tablet_portrait:16px;mobile_landscape:16px;mobile:16px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:2px;\" sub_heading_margin=\"margin-top:1px;\" sub_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\"]<em>Those Who Have Left Us Too Soon . . .</em>[/ultimate_heading][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]Life, on this earth, is not forever . . . and sometimes friends and family are taken from us before we are ready to see them go. Their influence on our lives hold special memories that sadden us because we can no longer enjoy their company. But in our memory of them, we are encouraged and uplifted by the times that we did have--listening, looking, and being in their presence. Reflect and remember those Tigers that were a part of our lives and share if you will any moments of your time together.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_type=\"bg_color\" bg_color_value=\"#eaeaea\"][vc_column][vc_masonry_grid post_type=\"gone-bfore\" max_items=\"-1\" style=\"load-more\" items_per_page=\"9\" gap=\"10\" orderby=\"modified\" order=\"ASC\" item=\"basicGrid_VerticalFlip\" btn_title=\"Show More...\" btn_style=\"classic\" btn_color=\"inverse\" grid_id=\"vc_gid:1531821360586-6aed5194-c89f-3\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"Testimonial \" spacer=\"line_only\" spacer_position=\"bottom\" line_height=\"1\" line_color=\"#eeee22\" main_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Allan|font_call:Allan|variant:700\" main_heading_style=\"font-style:italic;,font-weight:700;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:50px;tablet:30px;tablet_portrait:30px;mobile_landscape:16px;mobile:15px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-top:10px;\" line_width=\"50\"][/ultimate_heading][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][ve_testimonial_container][ve_testimonial_section photo=\"4459\" title=\"Robert Alvarado\" occupation=\"Sleep Tech \" testimonial_name_color=\"#dbef21\" testimonial_occupation_color=\"#82d646\"]We spent moments of time with these classmates, so they are a part of our history.  We may have spent hours with them personally or we may have just shared a common subject in the classroom.  I can remember each of these classmates, the look in their eyes and the way they carried themselves and treated others.  Mike Morton came to my house on one occasion and we put on some old boxing gloves.  Bad outcome for me.  But a good memory just the same.  Gary Martin was a fast runner like his younger brother and seemed to exhibit an air of assuredness.  I spent time at Bill Bailey\'s home as a cub scout and enjoyed his wit and enthusiasm.  Mary Powell had a quiet, peaceful demeanor as did Nan along with her quick, questioning mind. Mike DeMoss was sharp young man with a winning smile.  They left a mark--and a memory.[/ve_testimonial_section][ve_testimonial_section photo=\"402\" occupation=\"Professor \" testimonial_name_color=\"#dbef21\" testimonial_occupation_color=\"#82d646\"]Comments here.[/ve_testimonial_section][ve_testimonial_section photo=\"4463\" title=\"Hear me roar!\" occupation=\"Young tiger\" testimonial_name_color=\"#dbef21\" testimonial_occupation_color=\"#82d646\"]What I have to say is . . .[/ve_testimonial_section][ve_testimonial_section photo=\"4464\" title=\"I can Meow!\" occupation=\"Baby tiger\" testimonial_name_color=\"#dbef21\" testimonial_occupation_color=\"#82d646\"]I like to play.[/ve_testimonial_section][ve_testimonial_section photo=\"4458\" title=\"Trouble\" occupation=\"Master Mischiever\" testimonial_name_color=\"#dbef21\" testimonial_occupation_color=\"#82d646\"]I didn\'t do it.[/ve_testimonial_section][/ve_testimonial_container][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row]","Gone Before","","inherit","closed","closed","","12-autosave-v1","","","2018-07-17 10:00:59","2018-07-17 10:00:59","","12","http://1969tigers.co.events/s/12-autosave-v1/","0","revision","","0"),
