Mark your calendars!

Friday, Oct 5 @ 2 PM - 5 PM we Tigers will meet!                                            Where?   \'Food Shack\' restaurant at 4200 Airline Dr., Bossier City, LA  71111  (which is at the corner of Brownlee Rd. &amp; Airline Dr.)

At 5 PM, we will move to a room at Benton High School until the game at 7 PM.

Saturday, Oct 6 @ 9:30 AM, we will meet at IHOP at the Boardwalk for breakfast (670 Boardwalk Blvd.)  After breakfast, touring, shopping or just enjoying each others company.

