Now, submit words, pictures, sound bytes, videos--in any format normally used by Windows or Apple or Android.  If it is in some weird format, I may need for you to provide some details about the program that you used.  I know a good bit about computers, but I am older and move a little slower and still work for a living--so don\'t expect immediate publishing of what you send.  But participate--you can show your kids, grands and great-grands if you want--and share with them a little part of when you were their age.  It will also help your fellow classmates to know what has gone on--all these decades of time, so that if you get to come to this milestone reunion, you do not have to repeat your story multiple times.  Start today!

